# =============================================================================
# Why exclude these files?
# =============================================================================
# - node_modules: Will be rebuilt in container
# - .env files: Contain secrets, pass via environment variables
# - .git: Not needed in production image (adds 100+ MB)
# - test/docs: Not needed for runtime
# - IDE files: Developer-specific, not for production
# - *.md: Documentation not needed in container
#
# Result: Smaller build context = faster builds
# =============================================================================
